      "body" : "Didn&#39;t work for me with MariaDB until I changed the query string to <code>SELECT COUNT(*) FROM User WHERE u.name=:name</code> does (using asterisk).  Database error was: <code>Error in query (1054): Unknown column &#39;u&#39; in &#39;field list&#39;</code>"
