    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Thanks you all! Now it's work. <a href=\"https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAJPA-231\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">DATAJPA-231</a></p>\n\n<p>It will be nice if was possible to create count…By… methods just like find…By ones. Example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public interface UserRepository extends JpaRepository&lt;User, Long&gt; {\n\n   public Long /*or BigInteger */ countByActiveTrue();\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
