      "body" : "This version I like most - especially since I couldn&#39;t make a clue how this should work according to the docu :-) You saved my day :-) As a remark: Primitives (e.g. int) are included in the expamle-search, i.e. <code>int age</code> will be included although not set, but <code>Integer age</code> will be excluded from the sample (at least in Eclipselink)"
